display_long_description:
Synth Riders Demo will no longer be supported on Meta Quest devices and new users will no longer be able to search & install this app. If you already "own" this entitlement, you will continue to have access.

---------

A FREESTYLE-DANCE RHYTHM ALTERNATIVE

CUSTOM SONGS officially supported - never breaks with an update
GOOD FITNESS - activates whole body without repetitive movements
GREAT MUSIC – 74 free and 67 DLC songs from Gorillaz, Muse & more

In the demo, you can play 7 songs on all difficulty levels and experiment with all the modifiers - unlimited!

The full version of Synth Riders is available on the Meta Quest Store featuring:

• 135 Songs - 74 free and 67 DLC, including Gorillaz, Muse, Caravan Palace, The Offspring and more!
• Official Custom Song Support
• Cross-Platform Multiplayer
• 360° Spin Mode in Every Song
• Party mode - local multiplayer

We hope you will enjoy the demo and join the Synth Riders community soon!
